-- multimodal-api.fl — Multimodal HTTP API
-- Exposes endpoints that accept file uploads via multipart/form-data.
-- Deploy: fluent serve examples/multimodal-api.fl --port 8080 --cors
--
-- Endpoints:
--   POST /analyse-image    multipart field: image
--   POST /analyse-document multipart field: document
--   POST /transcribe       multipart field: audio
--   POST /smart-extract    multipart fields: image OR document (auto-detect)
--   POST /upload           generic — any file, runs full analysis

-- ── Image analysis endpoint ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
@expose(as: http, path: "/analyse-image", method: POST)
To analyse an uploaded image (image):
    @model(temperature: 0.3, max_tokens: 400)
    Ask claude to "Describe this image in detail. Note all objects, text, people, colours, and overall composition." using image image and call the result description.

    @model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 60, format: json)
    Ask openai/gpt-4o to "Return a JSON object with: category (string), has_text (boolean), has_people (boolean), dominant_colour (string), safe_for_work (boolean)." using image image and call the result metadata.

    Output description.
    Return a record with description description metadata metadata.
End of analyse an uploaded image.

-- ── Document Q&A endpoint ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@expose(as: http, path: "/analyse-document", method: POST)
To analyse an uploaded document (document):
    @model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 600, format: json)
    Ask claude to "Analyse this document and return JSON with: title, summary (2 sentences), key_points (list of 5), word_count_estimate (number), document_type (string)." using document document and call the result analysis.

    Output analysis.
    Return analysis.
End of analyse an uploaded document.

-- ── Audio transcription endpoint ─────────────────────────────────────────────
@expose(as: http, path: "/transcribe", method: POST)
To transcribe uploaded audio (audio):
    @model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 2000)
    Ask openai/gpt-4o to "Transcribe this audio. Return the full transcript with punctuation." using audio audio and call the result transcript.

    @model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 200)
    Ask claude to "Summarise this transcript in 2 sentences." using text transcript and call the result summary.

    Return a record with transcript transcript summary summary.
End of transcribe uploaded audio.

-- ── Smart extraction (auto-detect file type) ─────────────────────────────────
@expose(as: http, path: "/smart-extract", method: POST)
To smart extract from upload (file):
    @model(temperature: 0, max_tokens: 500, format: json)
    Ask claude to "Analyse this content and extract the most useful structured information. Return as JSON." using document file and call the result extracted.

    Return extracted.
End of smart extract from upload.
